### A. Complete Epic Change Structure

```
openspec/changes/epic-01-customer-management/
+-- .openspec.yaml
+-- proposal.md
+-- design.md
+-- tasks.md
+-- specs/
    +-- customer-registration/
    |   +-- spec.md
    +-- customer-profile/
    |   +-- spec.md
    +-- customer-segmentation/
    |   +-- spec.md
    +-- customer-events/
        +-- spec.md
```

### B. Complete HU Change Structure

